                        Mämhǝre Takla Hāymānot of Gänaḥti bought and donated the Ms. to the church of Gänaḥti Māryām in 1908 A.M. (= 1915-16 A.D.), during the reign of King Mǝnilǝk (r. 1889-1913).&#xD;
The children of Takla Hāymānot are called Gabra ʾƎsṭifānos, Walda Māryām, Gabra Yoḥannǝs, Gabra Ṣādǝq, Walatta Qirqos, Walatta Madḫǝn, Walatta Ṣādǝqān.
                     </colophon>
